<h2>Online Help for BANK BALANCE Object</h2>
<br></br> <br></br>    
This is an Object to manage Bank Balance for each Bank Account at accounting team.<br></br>
<ul>
1. Balance At Start/Balance At Closing<br></br> 
2. Amount received from customer in H B/L Shipment and not in H B/L Shipment related<br></br>
3. Amount paid to vendor in H B/L shipment and not in H B/L Shipment related <br></br>
</ul>
<br></br>

Record Types<br></br>
There are two record types in use.<br></br>
1.Local Currency Bank Account: Currency is local currency<br></br>
2.USD Bank Account: Currency is USD<br></br>
<br></br>
How to Check the detail receiptance from customers and payment to vendors.<br></br>
Go to Report Tab-->go to Accounting Management Folder->there are 4 reports as below name.<br></br>
1.Receiptance from customers-Local currency:BANK BALANCE-RECEIVED-LOCAL CUR<br></br>
2.Receiptance from customers-USD currency:BANK BALANCE-RECEIVED-USD<br></br>
3.Payment to vendors-Local currency:BANK BALANCE-PAID TO VENDOR-LOCAL CUR<br></br>
4.Payment to vendors-USD:BANK BALANCE-PAID TO VENDOR-USD<br></br>

 <br></br>
